Till you do not rot the drink a lot

00:52:09.120 --> 00:52:12.849
and the more it is rotten, the more it is costlier.

00:52:13.373 --> 00:52:16.866
If it has been rotten for the past fifty years
it is all the more better.

00:52:16.891 --> 00:52:20.909
And if it is a hundred year old, it is rare.

