00:53:07.932 --> 00:53:09.529
Drink more and more!

00:53:16.492 --> 00:53:19.118
This drinking and serving drinks to others

00:53:19.143 --> 00:53:22.628
is the custom of drinking that has started.

00:53:23.614 --> 00:53:25.416
I am scared of this.

00:53:25.441 --> 00:53:27.309
Manage Hanumanji

00:53:27.334 --> 00:53:29.317
Don't know what He will do.

00:53:30.241 --> 00:53:32.588
What disaster He may cause

00:53:32.613 --> 00:53:34.848
is unpredictable.

00:53:35.675 --> 00:53:40.521
I am afraid that one day He may put all the drunkards in the sea,

00:53:41.504 --> 00:53:47.006
because  He has mercy, devotion and everything

00:53:47.031 --> 00:53:49.746
but those who are against Him

00:53:49.771 --> 00:53:51.543
he is not for them.

00:53:51.822 --> 00:53:53.948
For example Shri Ganesha

00:53:53.973 --> 00:53:57.897
if anyone has a bad character

00:53:58.111 --> 00:54:01.312
if any one acts badly

00:54:01.359 --> 00:54:06.950
is attacked on his Mooladhara Chakra.

