But His case is different.

00:54:10.560 --> 00:54:17.095
When He sees that he is playing with his own consciousness

00:54:17.195 --> 00:54:25.706
by drinking- consciousness is lost- then He chases him.

00:54:26.211 --> 00:54:30.633
There will be conflict, quarrels and fights in homes

00:54:30.658 --> 00:54:33.487
and you see there will be fights on roads if you..

00:54:33.542 --> 00:54:35.260
NOT CLEAR..

