two drunkards will be hitting each other

00:54:40.882 --> 00:54:43.814
and then it spreads all the more.

00:54:43.839 --> 00:54:48.291
So Sahaja Yogis should not visit any drunkard's house

00:54:48.670 --> 00:54:51.143
that is an unholy place

00:54:51.168 --> 00:54:58.206
nor should keep any association with any drunkard.

00:55:00.393 --> 00:55:02.802
This is also fatal for Sahaja Yogis

00:55:02.827 --> 00:55:05.397
because on one hand you respect Hanumanji

00:55:05.422 --> 00:55:07.624
and on the other hand join drunkards.

00:55:12.844 --> 00:55:26.863
Especially in Poona, I don't know
how many types of Hanumanjis have come  here,

00:55:26.888 --> 00:55:32.042
people living in Poona should be very alert.

