They asked, “Why Mother?"

00:55:43.096 --> 00:55:47.598
I told them that after having a drink you sing silly movie songs.

00:55:47.623 --> 00:55:51.405
Do you know who is this Maruti?

00:55:51.430 --> 00:55:53.631
When He will strangle throats of all of you

00:55:53.656 --> 00:55:55.523
then only you will come to know.

00:55:55.548 --> 00:56:02.430
I have heard about Ganpati programs
that  they don't allow anyone to drink.

00:56:02.737 --> 00:56:05.216
They drive away those who drink.

00:56:05.241 --> 00:56:06.767
Just think,

00:56:06.792 --> 00:56:09.146
see their courage!

00:56:09.171 --> 00:56:13.149
In front of Hanumanji, they do all this business

00:56:13.174 --> 00:56:16.566
In front of Hanumanji!

00:56:17.617 --> 00:56:20.053
What a courage!

00:56:21.680 --> 00:56:23.550
and this

00:56:23.968 --> 00:56:25.788
by doing everything

