We will say, what is there so much in drinking

00:56:58.509 --> 00:57:02.219
because it is Shri Hanumanji's case.

00:57:02.623 --> 00:57:06.869
What is the reason you are going against Hanumanji?

00:57:07.204 --> 00:57:11.177
His power flows through your right side.

00:57:11.202 --> 00:57:14.449
Use that in balance.

00:57:14.474 --> 00:57:18.859
instead of upsetting your liver, spoil this and spoil that.

00:57:18.875 --> 00:57:20.413
He will definitely get upset.

00:57:21.015 --> 00:57:24.259
That means it is Hanumanji's job in subtle.

00:57:25.878 --> 00:57:29.478
People don't understand this in reality.

00:57:29.676 --> 00:57:31.655
In reality it is such

00:57:31.680 --> 00:57:33.774
that if you say something against drinking

00:57:33.799 --> 00:57:36.749
people will run to kill you.

00:57:37.503 --> 00:57:38.470
If you don't drink

00:57:38.495 --> 00:57:41.091
they will say you are a fool that you don't drink.

